data.description: Come see this great home located in a cul-de-sac in the coveted Stathams Landing! 4 bed, 2.5 bath PLUS a large bonus room!! The main floor has large kitchen with stainless steel appliances, island and eat-in area. Also on main floor is a formal dining room, office, living room with wood burning fireplace, half bath and laundry room. Upstairs you'll find all the bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a large bonus room perfect for another bedroom, living room, home gym, man(lady)cave,etc. Large master bedroom with vaulted ceilings has en suite bathroom with dual vanity, whirlpool tub and separate shower. This house sits on a great sized lot with a beautiful back patio that's perfect to sit and enjoy yourself as the kids and/or pets play in the large fenced in yard. Don't forget this home is located on the highly rated Southern Landings Golf Course! Members of the course get access to a beautiful pool, tennis court, and nice bar.
